snippet.textDisplay:
Pakistan national anthem for those who don't know Urdu
==============================================

Blessed be the sacred land
     Happy be the the bounteous realm

Symbol of high revolve, Land of Pakistan
    Blessed be thou citadel of faith

The order of the sacred land
    Is the might of the brotherhood of the people

May the nation, and the country, and the state
    Shine in glory everlasting

Blessed to be goal of our ambition
    This flag of the crescent and the star

Leads the way to progress and perfection
   Interpreter of our past, glory of our present

Inspiration of our future
    Symbol of Almighty's protection
